    "Manually curating genomic repositories and annotating genetic relationships from literature is time-consuming and challenging [8].",
    "Traditional reading and summarising lack scalability, are subject to personal interpretations, and are time-consuming.",
    "Automating the preprocessing of scientific literature and post-processing of extracted information using Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques can address these limitations.",
